Package: libaspell
Section: libs
Priority: optional
Architecture: ARCH
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: provides a spell checking API
 This package provides libaspell, a shared library which
 provides spell checking routines.

Package: aspell
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: ARCH
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: aspell userspace tools
 This package provides commandline spell checking tools.

Package: libaspell-dev
Section: libdevel
Provides: aspell-dev
Priority: optional
Architecture: ARCH
Depends: aspell (= ${binary:Version}), libncursesw-dev
Description: aspell headers and static library
 This package provides the aspell static library, headers 
 and pkgconfig data required to build applications, or 
 plugins which use the Aspell API.

